                                        MCPAREA
                                        ORCMCPAREA
                                        MCPDATA-REC.
      *
           MOVE    "DBDISCONNECT"      TO  MCP-FUNC.
           CALL    "ORCMCPSUB"          USING
                                        MCPAREA
                                        ORCMCPAREA
                                        MCPDATA-REC.
           .
       900-DBCLOSE-EXT.
           EXIT.
